262
00:14:35,638 --> 00:14:38,752
That is impossible! Hahaha!

263
00:14:38,753 --> 00:14:40,526
No way, right?

264
00:14:40,839 --> 00:14:42,766
Don't scare me like that.

265
00:14:44,485 --> 00:14:47,219
Lord Veldora! Look at that!

266
00:14:48,695 --> 00:14:52,028
Seems like Rimuru's evolution into a Demon Lord is finally over.

267
00:14:53,564 --> 00:14:54,676
What's that?

268
00:14:54,701 --> 00:14:56,103
Must be "Gift."

269
00:14:56,104 --> 00:14:57,521
When you evolve into a Demon Lord,

270
00:14:57,522 --> 00:15:03,401
a Gift will be distributed to all monsters within your genealogy.

271
00:15:03,402 --> 00:15:04,997
I see.

272
00:15:09,424 --> 00:15:11,221
L-Lord Veldora!

273
00:15:11,246 --> 00:15:13,738
Why? How did this happen?

274
00:15:13,851 --> 00:15:19,137
Lord Veldora, this person whom we thought were Lord Rimuru... could it be...?

275
00:15:19,181 --> 00:15:21,837
-I noticed from the start, though. -Eh?

276
00:15:21,862 --> 00:15:26,246
I already realized that Rimuru's skill was special from the start.

277
00:15:26,271 --> 00:15:28,729
Yes, that it is an independent type.

278
00:15:28,754 --> 00:15:33,703
As I expect from you, Lord Veldora... or so you think I will say?!

279
00:15:33,728 --> 00:15:37,394
Up until now, you've always been smug when you explain stuff to me.

280
00:15:37,395 --> 00:15:40,327
Ifrit, Shion and orders are waking up!

281
00:15:40,352 --> 00:15:41,837
However...

282
00:15:48,156 --> 00:15:50,283
L-Lord Raphael?!

283
00:15:53,077 --> 00:15:57,254
