285
00:16:00,877 --> 00:16:05,709
No matter what it is, I, Ifrit, shall obey your every command!

286
00:16:05,882 --> 00:16:10,552
Yes. The species Ifrit has no name and a weak ego.

287
00:16:10,553 --> 00:16:13,972
Therefore, you do not possess sufficient foundation to obtain a skill.

288
00:16:13,973 --> 00:16:16,224
I recommend you to resume your training.

289
00:16:16,225 --> 00:16:17,385
Roger!

290
00:16:17,410 --> 00:16:21,004
I, Ifrit, shall now begin my training!

291
00:16:21,673 --> 00:16:24,025
One, two, three, four, five!

292
00:16:24,050 --> 00:16:25,150
Ummm...

293
00:16:25,151 --> 00:16:26,068
Report.

294
00:16:26,069 --> 00:16:29,697
I am convinced that the individual Veldora has been slacking off too much.

295
00:16:30,615 --> 00:16:31,593
Order.

296
00:16:31,617 --> 00:16:34,576
Acquire Ultimate skill immediately.

297
00:16:34,577 --> 00:16:36,745
But that's kind of impossible...

298
00:16:36,746 --> 00:16:38,538
Report. It's possible.

299
00:16:38,539 --> 00:16:41,917
I've expanded this computing space by force.

300
00:16:41,918 --> 00:16:44,353
You shall maintain this space by yourself

301
00:16:44,377 --> 00:16:47,385
while continuing your work analyzing the Unlimited Imprisonment.

302
00:16:47,410 --> 00:16:52,852
She didn't ask whether I can do it or not, so that means it's an order.

303
00:16:57,058 --> 00:16:59,059
We must do it, I guess.

304
00:16:59,060 --> 00:17:00,102
Yes!

305
00:17:01,646 --> 00:17:05,023
I did my best and finally acquire one!

306
00:17:05,024 --> 00:17:07,767
My Ultimate skill, Faust!

307
00:17:07,827 --> 00:17:12,155
It's thanks to this Gift from Rimuru, I must thank him later.

308
00:17:12,156 --> 00:17:15,033
Now Lord Raphael won't be yelling at us.

309
00:17:15,034 --> 00:17:16,451
Yeah.

310
00:17:16,452 --> 00:17:19,833
And also, Ifrit, you got a lot more muscular, aren't you?

311
00:17:19,858 --> 00:17:22,386
No, I still have more to go.

312
00:17:22,411 --> 00:17:26,709
I will train harder and lower my body fat percentage to 10%!

313
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:29,050
I see. Well, do your best.

314
00:17:29,966 --> 00:17:31,007
Question.

315
00:17:31,008 --> 00:17:33,635
Have you acquired an Ultimate Skill?

316
00:17:33,636 --> 00:17:35,189
Yes of course!

317
00:17:35,214 --> 00:17:36,274
Good.

318
00:17:36,299 --> 00:17:39,725
Well then, let's break this Unlimited Imprisonment right away.

319
00:17:40,848 --> 00:17:44,823
Now you can finally get out! Congratulation, Lord Veldora!

320
00:17:44,848 --> 00:17:48,105
It's still too early to celebrate, though. Hahaha!

321
00:17:48,461 --> 00:17:51,508
What should I talk about with Rimuru after I break free?

322
00:17:51,779 --> 00:17:53,446
I'll start with a boast!

323
00:17:53,447 --> 00:17:57,450
For that, I will pretend that I don't know anything that happened outside.

324
00:17:57,451 --> 00:17:59,870
That sounds good.

325
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:05,166
Maybe I can pretend to acquire Faust in front of him.

326
00:18:05,167 --> 00:18:09,017
"O-Oooh! So this is what my evolved skill is like?!"

327
00:18:09,042 --> 00:18:14,092
"My Unique Skill Inquirer have became Ultimate Skill Faust!"

328
00:18:14,093 --> 00:18:18,972
"It is a power that embodies my restless pursuit of knowledge!"

329
00:18:18,973 --> 00:18:20,507
That's what I'll say.

330
00:18:20,532 --> 00:18:21,850
"That's amazing, Veldora!"

331
00:18:21,851 --> 00:18:24,700
"You just got an Ultimate Skill so easily!"

332
00:18:24,725 --> 00:18:27,105
"As I thought, you're an incredible dude!"

333
00:18:27,130 --> 00:18:31,192
