334
00:18:31,193 --> 00:18:34,029
After that, I will say this to him.

335
00:18:34,030 --> 00:18:36,237
"It's no big deal."

336
00:18:38,951 --> 00:18:43,788
Ummm, Lord Veldora, if I may...

337
00:18:43,789 --> 00:18:47,513
If you're going to go outside and stand as Lord Rimuru's friend,

338
00:18:47,538 --> 00:18:52,005
Lord Rimuru will have to take responsibility for your action.

339
00:18:52,006 --> 00:18:54,382
Please remember that.

340
00:18:54,383 --> 00:18:57,591
People have this thing called "Unwelcome favor."

341
00:18:57,616 --> 00:19:02,859
It means things that you do out of goodwill can still be an annoyance for others.

342
00:19:03,137 --> 00:19:05,602
And for someone as powerful as you,

343
00:19:05,603 --> 00:19:09,356
I believe it's better if you first consult with others before you start.

344
00:19:09,357 --> 00:19:10,751
I see.

345
00:19:11,132 --> 00:19:14,819
Understand? You don't want Lord Rimuru to hate you, don't you?

346
00:19:14,820 --> 00:19:16,279
I'll cry.

347
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:18,490
As such, you need to be cautious,

348
00:19:18,491 --> 00:19:22,183
careful, thoughtful, and think about others.

349
00:19:22,244 --> 00:19:23,511
It's a promise.

350
00:19:23,536 --> 00:19:25,360
Yes, I understand.

351
00:19:25,385 --> 00:19:28,208
And Ifrit, I will promise you this.

352
00:19:28,209 --> 00:19:29,793
Promise?

353
00:19:29,794 --> 00:19:34,881
I promise that someday I will free you from that place.

354
00:19:34,882 --> 00:19:39,353
R-Really?! I will eagerly wait for that day to come!

355
00:19:39,378 --> 00:19:41,314
Rest assured, Ifrit.

356
00:19:41,339 --> 00:19:45,725
Like Rimuru, I'm the type who always keeps his promise.

357
00:19:45,726 --> 00:19:51,481
And I'm sure it won't take long until I fulfill our promise.

358
00:19:51,482 --> 00:19:53,650
I'll be looking forward to be with you again.

359
00:19:53,675 --> 00:19:55,443
Yes, of course!

360
00:19:55,444 --> 00:19:58,381
When that time comes, please have another shogi match with me.

361
00:19:58,406 --> 00:19:59,987
I won't hold back.

362
00:20:00,012 --> 00:20:01,742
Just as I want it!

363
00:20:11,335 --> 00:20:14,093
This place sure takes me back.

364
00:20:18,563 --> 00:20:20,525
It has been two years since then.

365
00:20:20,550 --> 00:20:21,705
Report.

366
00:20:21,730 --> 00:20:24,855
Analysis and Assessment of Unlimited Imprisonment is complete.

367
00:20:25,004 --> 00:20:27,200
I can finally fulfill my promise.

368
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:28,928
I will free you now.

369
00:20:29,311 --> 00:20:30,612
Veldora!

370
00:20:34,396 --> 00:20:37,235
I grew taller?!

371
00:20:38,904 --> 00:20:41,614
Raphael, make a Body Double of me.

372
00:20:41,615 --> 00:20:43,658
I'll make it as the vessel for Veldora.

373
00:20:43,659 --> 00:20:45,516
Enhanced Replication activate.

374
00:20:51,167 --> 00:20:54,049
My body did grew a bit.

375
00:20:57,590 --> 00:21:01,167
It's supposed to be me, but man, I look beautiful.

376
00:21:04,162 --> 00:21:05,664
Okay, let's do this.

377
00:21:28,216 --> 00:21:29,900
Please work.

378
00:21:32,215 --> 00:21:33,215
Report.

379
00:21:33,240 --> 00:21:37,777
The soul corridor between Master and the individual Veldora has been established.

380
00:21:56,254 --> 00:22:01,635
I, the Storm Dragon Veldora Tempest, have returned!

381
00:22:02,229 --> 00:22:06,089
Anyone who opposes me will die!

382
00:22:19,144 --> 00:22:22,522
I'm used to losing things

